WEBVTT

00:00:00.060 --> 00:00:04.258
All right,

00:00:01.319 --> 00:00:06.540
I was praying and the Lord told me

00:00:04.259 --> 00:00:08.460
this. I don't know who this is for,

00:00:06.540 --> 00:00:11.280
but it's for somebody

00:00:08.460 --> 00:00:13.380
because I was praying

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:15.540
and the Lord told me, 'I want you

00:00:13.380 --> 00:00:17.039
to tell them what I told you about

00:00:15.540 --> 00:00:18.960
healing.'I

00:00:17.039 --> 00:00:22.080
said, 'Okay,'so

00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:27.240
here you go, whoever this is for.

00:00:22.080 --> 00:00:29.339
I was talking to some people whose

00:00:27.240 --> 00:00:31.320
husband goes to our

00:00:29.340 --> 00:00:34.019
church. I worked on the staff at Victory

00:00:31.320 --> 00:00:37.399
Church here in Oklahoma

00:00:34.020 --> 00:00:40.700
City for a long time.

00:00:37.399 --> 00:00:40.700
I

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:45.360
was talking to some more people there on

00:00:43.020 --> 00:00:50.579
staff, and a woman's husband was suffering from

00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:52.739
some severe arthritis—really bad.

00:00:52.739 --> 00:00:57.839
His name was Stanley, and he told me,

00:00:55.140 --> 00:01:00.539
'Hey, Brandon, how come not

00:00:57.840 --> 00:01:03.660
all Christians are healed when they pray,

00:01:00.539 --> 00:01:04.979
and we suffer so long with stuff?'It

00:01:03.660 --> 00:01:07.320
was

00:01:04.979 --> 00:01:09.299
kind of a

00:01:07.320 --> 00:01:11.759
challenging question and I didn't

00:01:09.299 --> 00:01:14.100
really have the answer for it, so I

00:01:11.760 --> 00:01:16.200
said, 'Well, I'll pray about it. I

00:01:14.100 --> 00:01:18.119
don't understand why people go through

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:19.860
what they go through, other than that we

00:01:18.119 --> 00:01:22.020
live in a fallen world.'I

00:01:19.860 --> 00:01:24.720
said, 'I'll pray about this.'I

00:01:22.020 --> 00:01:26.640
started interceding

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:28.560
for this. Well, it was not very long after;

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:30.119
I was sitting on the edge of my

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:32.220
bed getting ready for

00:01:30.119 --> 00:01:34.799
bed, and I just asked in my heart,

00:01:32.220 --> 00:01:37.979
'Lord, why are not all Christians healed

00:01:34.799 --> 00:01:39.960
like they should be? I would

00:01:37.979 --> 00:01:41.400
like to understand more; give me

00:01:39.960 --> 00:01:45.419
revelation.'I

00:01:41.400 --> 00:01:48.240
went to bed, and all of a sudden—I

00:01:45.420 --> 00:01:50.040
can't explain it to you, it's very

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:52.259
similar to how I went there when he took me

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:55.380
to the Tribulation—I

00:01:52.259 --> 00:01:57.360
was taken out of my body

00:01:55.380 --> 00:02:00.899
and

00:01:57.360 --> 00:02:05.159
I was at the foot of the cross, at

00:02:00.899 --> 00:02:07.200
his crucifixion.

00:02:09.538 --> 00:02:16.200
He was tied to a whipping post.

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:18.899
There was a Roman soldier with all this

00:02:16.200 --> 00:02:20.879
Roman garb on, standing on

00:02:18.900 --> 00:02:23.940
his left hand.

00:02:20.879 --> 00:02:26.160
He was chained up with his

00:02:23.940 --> 00:02:28.920
hands just like this on a whipping post.

00:02:26.160 --> 00:02:31.020
His

00:02:28.920 --> 00:02:33.780
hands were chained up

00:02:31.020 --> 00:02:36.599
with rope, and his hands were up

00:02:33.780 --> 00:02:39.000
on that whipping post.

00:02:36.599 --> 00:02:41.940
I can tell you the temperature in

00:02:39.000 --> 00:02:44.640
that area; there was

00:02:41.940 --> 00:02:47.280
a dirt floor there, and the whipping

00:02:44.640 --> 00:02:49.920
post

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:52.739
was wood.

00:02:49.920 --> 00:02:55.679
The temperature was about 85 degrees

00:02:52.739 --> 00:02:57.959
outside, maybe 80. I could tell you

00:02:55.680 --> 00:03:01.140
because I could smell the

00:02:57.959 --> 00:03:03.840
livestock in

00:03:01.140 --> 00:03:05.819
this coliseum area. I don't know what it

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:08.160
was; I could see

00:03:05.819 --> 00:03:10.260
these people right here and they were

00:03:08.160 --> 00:03:14.280
watching him.

00:03:10.260 --> 00:03:16.739
This other man on this side

00:03:14.280 --> 00:03:19.319
was wearing a black outfit;

00:03:16.739 --> 00:03:21.540
he was a

00:03:19.319 --> 00:03:24.359
big man, probably 400 pounds.

00:03:21.540 --> 00:03:27.480
He was a massive man—he wasn't

00:03:24.360 --> 00:03:28.680
overweight, he was muscular and

00:03:27.480 --> 00:03:32.220
looked huge.

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:34.860
He took that cat-of-nine-tails, and

00:03:32.220 --> 00:03:40.200
this other one took this canine. Jesus'back—he

00:03:34.860 --> 00:03:42.360
was a young man.

00:03:40.200 --> 00:03:44.879
You see all this

00:03:42.360 --> 00:03:49.019
stuff on TV where he looks old, but

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:53.099
no, he was a young guy,

00:03:49.019 --> 00:03:54.780
30 or 33 years old. In

00:03:53.099 --> 00:03:56.940
your mind you're thinking he's

00:03:54.780 --> 00:04:00.239
old because of pictures, but no, he was young.

00:03:56.940 --> 00:04:04.260
His back

00:04:00.239 --> 00:04:06.239
had oily skin; he had dirt on him

00:04:04.260 --> 00:04:08.700
from the

00:04:06.239 --> 00:04:10.920
sweat, and

00:04:08.700 --> 00:04:14.159
you could see the dirt on his back. He was dirty, and it was

00:04:10.920 --> 00:04:17.219
oily, olive-looking

00:04:14.159 --> 00:04:21.298
skin. Then they took

00:04:17.220 --> 00:04:24.240
though cat-of-nine-tails

00:04:21.298 --> 00:04:26.520
and they whipped him one time with it on

00:04:24.240 --> 00:04:31.560
this side, and then this one whipped him

00:04:26.520 --> 00:04:34.139
on this side, and he screamed out in

00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:37.199
agony. I watched it and I started

00:04:34.139 --> 00:04:39.540
screaming and yelling, 'Stop

00:04:37.199 --> 00:04:43.199
this! Stop this!'but nobody could hear me.

00:04:39.540 --> 00:04:45.660
But Jesus was watching—Jesus himself was

00:04:43.199 --> 00:04:46.740
with me. I was standing outside

00:04:45.660 --> 00:04:48.960
of my body; I don't know how this

00:04:46.740 --> 00:04:53.580
happened, but Jesus was standing

00:04:48.960 --> 00:04:56.280
right here by me and he was

00:04:53.580 --> 00:04:59.460
watching himself be crucified.

00:04:56.280 --> 00:05:02.698
One man was whipping him,

00:04:59.460 --> 00:05:05.638
and Jesus's face looked up at

00:05:02.699 --> 00:05:06.840
them and he said (I'm going to do this

00:05:05.639 --> 00:05:09.060
without crying),

00:05:06.840 --> 00:05:12.138
'I love you.

00:05:17.100 --> 00:05:21.540
I love you. I love you.'And he kept telling them

00:05:19.199 --> 00:05:24.720
that every single time.

00:05:21.540 --> 00:05:27.060
They were mocking him

00:05:24.720 --> 00:05:29.160
and they grabbed a hold of his beard,

00:05:27.060 --> 00:05:32.900
and I saw them rip huge

00:05:29.160 --> 00:05:37.199
chunks of his beard out of his face.

00:05:32.900 --> 00:05:40.258
They kept going at it, and it was almost

00:05:37.199 --> 00:05:44.510
like they were having fun; it was sick.

00:05:40.259 --> 00:05:46.139
They took those whips

00:05:46.139 --> 00:05:50.280
and they were just beating his flesh

00:05:48.180 --> 00:05:52.979
with it and it was tearing him

00:05:50.280 --> 00:05:55.198
to pieces. He had chunks

00:05:52.979 --> 00:05:58.320
of flesh hanging down off of his body

00:05:55.199 --> 00:06:00.120
and it was just dangling down. It

00:05:58.320 --> 00:06:04.199
was the most grotesque thing I've ever

00:06:00.120 --> 00:06:07.020
seen in my life and blood was everywhere.

00:06:04.199 --> 00:06:08.340
And he looked at me—this Jesus, when he

00:06:07.020 --> 00:06:10.198
was standing right here—he looked at me

00:06:08.340 --> 00:06:13.099
and he said,

00:06:10.199 --> 00:06:13.100
'Brandon,

00:06:15.740 --> 00:06:21.720
what more?'No,

00:06:18.840 --> 00:06:25.940
he said this to me—I want to quote

00:06:21.720 --> 00:06:25.940
it exactly the way he said it—he said,

00:06:27.300 --> 00:06:34.319
'If somebody was to ask you

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:36.360
and challenge you about your faith,

00:06:34.319 --> 00:06:38.039
saying that you're saved,

00:06:36.360 --> 00:06:40.080
and they said, "We don't really believe

00:06:38.039 --> 00:06:43.560
you're saved; you're not going to go to heaven,"you

00:06:40.080 --> 00:06:46.080
would fight them with

00:06:43.560 --> 00:06:47.699
every single thing. "Yes, I believe I'm saved!"You

00:06:46.080 --> 00:06:49.500
would argue with

00:06:47.699 --> 00:06:52.020
them; you would go after them.'That is what he

00:06:49.500 --> 00:06:53.220
said. I said, 'Yes, that's right,'because

00:06:52.020 --> 00:06:55.560
I don't question that at

00:06:53.220 --> 00:06:57.860
all in my heart.

00:06:55.560 --> 00:07:01.740
He said,

00:06:57.860 --> 00:07:05.160
'Healing is no different than your

00:07:01.740 --> 00:07:08.100
salvation. I took your sin on my

00:07:05.160 --> 00:07:11.479
body and I took your sickness.'And

00:07:08.100 --> 00:07:15.740
he said, 'What do you not understand?

00:07:11.479 --> 00:07:19.039
By my stripes

00:07:15.740 --> 00:07:21.860
you are healed.

00:07:19.039 --> 00:07:26.219
By my stripes

00:07:21.860 --> 00:07:30.180
you are healed.'And he said, 'When you

00:07:26.220 --> 00:07:33.180
believe in my healing power as much as

00:07:30.180 --> 00:07:36.860
you believe in my salvation, then

00:07:33.180 --> 00:07:36.860
the manifestation will come.

00:07:39.180 --> 00:07:43.919
You've got to believe it that strong.'That is

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:46.800
what he was telling me.

00:07:43.919 --> 00:07:49.440
'Believe in what I did for you.

00:07:49.440 --> 00:07:56.280
What more do you need? I took it

00:07:52.560 --> 00:07:58.800
all on my body for you. I took sickness; I

00:07:56.280 --> 00:08:00.659
took disease for you.

00:07:58.800 --> 00:08:03.900
I took it on me;

00:08:00.660 --> 00:08:05.160
by my stripes you're healed.'I saw

00:08:03.900 --> 00:08:07.318
his stripes.

00:08:05.160 --> 00:08:09.720
I saw him. I could hear the people

00:08:07.319 --> 00:08:13.319
yelling in the background,

00:08:09.720 --> 00:08:16.680
'Crucify him! Crucify him!'and he was

00:08:13.319 --> 00:08:18.479
beaten to a pulp for us

00:08:16.680 --> 00:08:21.000
so that we don't have to have sickness

00:08:18.479 --> 00:08:22.500
in our bodies, so we don't have to suffer

00:08:21.000 --> 00:08:27.060
with it.

00:08:22.500 --> 00:08:28.080
By his stripes you are healed. And I saw

00:08:27.060 --> 00:08:30.960
it.

00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:33.539
He was beaten and he was bruised for our

00:08:30.960 --> 00:08:34.799
iniquities; the chastisement of our peace

00:08:33.539 --> 00:08:40.080
was upon him,

00:08:34.799 --> 00:08:42.659
and with his stripes you are healed.

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:44.279
Believe it as much as you believe in

00:08:42.659 --> 00:08:46.620
your salvation.

00:08:44.279 --> 00:08:48.060
If anybody was to talk to you, try to

00:08:46.620 --> 00:08:49.800
talk you out of it, saying, 'You're not saved,'the

00:08:48.060 --> 00:08:51.660
same way

00:08:49.800 --> 00:08:54.000
you're healed—if

00:08:51.660 --> 00:08:57.360
anybody should try to tell you you're

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:59.040
not healed, you would tell them, 'No, I'm healed.'And

00:08:57.360 --> 00:09:01.200
you've got to believe it that much

00:08:59.040 --> 00:09:04.199
inside of you. You cannot doubt in your

00:09:01.200 --> 00:09:07.620
heart; don't doubt your heart. Believe it

00:09:04.200 --> 00:09:09.660
with all your might; believe it like you

00:09:07.620 --> 00:09:12.360
believe in your salvation. It's so much

00:09:09.660 --> 00:09:15.079
more. We have all those sins—we just

00:09:12.360 --> 00:09:18.839
take it

00:09:15.080 --> 00:09:22.440
for granted that we are

00:09:18.839 --> 00:09:24.300
saved, whenever all the

00:09:22.440 --> 00:09:25.800
things they used to do to forgive sins,

00:09:24.300 --> 00:09:28.800
to atone for sins—killing

00:09:25.800 --> 00:09:30.359
animals, goats, and calves, and all

00:09:28.800 --> 00:09:33.240
the stuff they did to wash the

00:09:30.360 --> 00:09:35.220
sins away of the people...

00:09:33.240 --> 00:09:37.620
we just go to him and ask him for

00:09:35.220 --> 00:09:39.180
forgiveness, and he said he's faithful

00:09:37.620 --> 00:09:41.100
and just to forgive us and cleanse us

00:09:39.180 --> 00:09:43.079
from all unrighteousness. But we just

00:09:41.100 --> 00:09:45.420
believe that, and it's simple. We just

00:09:43.080 --> 00:09:48.360
believe God: "You saved me, You washed

00:09:45.420 --> 00:09:50.880
my sins away."But the same faith it

00:09:48.360 --> 00:09:52.740
took to do that—which we realize how

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:55.860
much it probably was to wash all those

00:09:52.740 --> 00:10:00.300
things away—it took a sacrifice of

00:09:55.860 --> 00:10:02.519
Jesus. He took our sickness in His body;

00:10:00.300 --> 00:10:05.640
then He took our poverty. He said He

00:10:02.519 --> 00:10:09.660
became poor that we might be rich; He

00:10:05.640 --> 00:10:12.779
became sick; He became all these things.

00:10:09.660 --> 00:10:15.540
Look at it, just believe it, and He said,

00:10:12.779 --> 00:10:17.760
"Believe it with all your heart, Brandon."I

00:10:15.540 --> 00:10:21.300
don't know who that's for,

00:10:17.760 --> 00:10:24.240
but I had that, and I came back.

00:10:21.300 --> 00:10:25.920
When I got back and I woke up the next

00:10:24.240 --> 00:10:28.440
day,

00:10:25.920 --> 00:10:30.920
I cried and cried

00:10:33.660 --> 00:10:39.540
because

00:10:39.540 --> 00:10:44.760
it was horrific what He went through.

00:10:42.180 --> 00:10:47.819
So Jesus did that for you.

00:10:44.760 --> 00:10:48.540
Jesus died for you, and He loves you so

00:10:47.820 --> 00:10:51.060
much.

00:10:48.540 --> 00:10:53.399
I saw those people whipping Him, and He

00:10:51.060 --> 00:10:55.920
kept telling them, "I love you,

00:10:53.399 --> 00:10:57.360
I love you."When most people would just

00:10:55.920 --> 00:10:58.740
want to spit on those other people—they

00:10:57.360 --> 00:11:01.140
were spitting on Him, they were doing all

00:10:58.740 --> 00:11:03.300
bad things, shoving that crown of

00:11:01.140 --> 00:11:06.600
thorns on His head—and

00:11:03.300 --> 00:11:09.479
He just kept saying, "I love you."And

00:11:06.600 --> 00:11:12.300
I just want to tell everybody: Jesus

00:11:09.480 --> 00:11:15.000
really does love you,

00:11:12.300 --> 00:11:17.099
and He doesn't want you to suffer. He

00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:19.440
wants you to be blessed.

00:11:17.100 --> 00:11:22.200
Beloved, I wish above all things that you

00:11:19.440 --> 00:11:24.480
prosper and be in health even as your soul

00:11:22.200 --> 00:11:26.820
prospers.

00:11:24.480 --> 00:11:28.680
So I want you to have a blessed day.

00:11:26.820 --> 00:11:30.600
Father, we just thank You, Lord, for these

00:11:28.680 --> 00:11:33.060
people right now. We just pray healing

00:11:30.600 --> 00:11:36.480
over their bodies, and we thank You,

00:11:33.060 --> 00:11:40.079
Father, for a turnaround in their

00:11:36.480 --> 00:11:42.899
circumstances right now. In Jesus'name, we

00:11:40.079 --> 00:11:46.199
pronounce healing and wholeness and

00:11:42.899 --> 00:11:48.300
wellness over their bodies. And we thank

00:11:46.200 --> 00:11:51.899
You, Lord, for Your healing power going

00:11:48.300 --> 00:11:54.240
through them in the name of Jesus.

00:11:51.899 --> 00:11:57.360
From the top of their head to the soles

00:11:54.240 --> 00:12:00.600
of their feet, they are healed by the

00:11:57.360 --> 00:12:03.959
stripes of Jesus. And we take authority

00:12:00.600 --> 00:12:06.839
over sickness and disease. We take

00:12:03.959 --> 00:12:09.180
authority over poverty. We take authority

00:12:06.839 --> 00:12:12.420
over lack, not enough, and barely getting

00:12:09.180 --> 00:12:15.359
by. We take authority over it and we say

00:12:12.420 --> 00:12:18.240
it's under our feet in the name of Jesus.

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:21.120
And we thank You, Lord, for Your healing

00:12:18.240 --> 00:12:24.720
power that delivers us from all sickness,

00:12:21.120 --> 00:12:27.660
all disease in the name of Jesus Christ.

00:12:24.720 --> 00:12:29.700
And we call you whole and healed and

00:12:27.660 --> 00:12:32.040
well in Jesus'name.

00:12:29.700 --> 00:12:35.579
Now

00:12:32.040 --> 00:12:37.860
comment down below if there's a witness

00:12:35.579 --> 00:12:40.560
with you, if you're that person

00:12:37.860 --> 00:12:42.240
that I was talking to, because I really

00:12:40.560 --> 00:12:46.439
believe the Lord wanted me to tell you.

00:12:42.240 --> 00:12:49.320
And I hope my words gave what He

00:12:46.440 --> 00:12:52.980
did for us a little justice, because

00:12:49.320 --> 00:12:56.160
I know it's all so short of it. In my

00:12:52.980 --> 00:12:57.180
heart, I want to... get it across to the

00:12:56.160 --> 00:13:02.420
people

00:12:57.180 --> 00:13:02.420
and so have a blessed day y'all bye-bye

